@startuml
title 传感器数据可靠上传 - 分批上传未同步数据

participant "WorkManager" as WM
participant "SensorUploadWorker" as Worker
participant "RawDataDao" as Dao
participant "Uploader" as Uploader
database "Room" as DB
participant "Netlify API" as API

WM -> Worker: 触发 doWork() (定期或手动)
loop 分批处理 (batchSize=50)
    Worker -> Dao: getUnsyncedBatch(limit)
    Dao -> DB: SELECT ... LIMIT
    DB --> Dao: 返回最多50条
    Dao --> Worker: List<RawDataEntity>
    Worker -> Worker: 构造 JSON 数组
    Worker -> Uploader: execute(UploadRequest)
    Uploader -> API: POST /api/sensor-data
    API --> Uploader: Response (200)
    Uploader --> Worker: Result.success
    Worker -> Dao: update(synced = true)
    Dao -> DB: UPDATE
end
Worker --> WM: Result.success
@enduml
